criteria.inclusion_criteria:
1. Aged 12 to 55 years;
2. Patients undergoing allogeneic hematopoietic stem cell transplantation for  hematology diseases;
3. Seronegative for CMV IgM; negative for CMV DNA in blood and urine;
4. Understand and voluntarily sign an informed consent.

criteria.exclusion_criteria:
1. Absolute neutrophil count <0.5*10^9/L,platelet count <25*10^9/L;
2. serum creatinine > 105umol/L; ALT, AST and total bilirubin> 2 times upper limit of normal value;
3. Ongoing antiviral treatment with acyclovir,ganciclovir or foscarnet;
4. Allergy to foscarnet or ganciclovir;
5. Pregnant or lactating women.
